												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[GERRY] Gortash takes a little step forward and addresses the partriars in the room arms out wide. At ‘Dearest Raven..’ Gortash turns round 180 degrees to address Ravenguard who is still at the top of the stairs that the ceremony will now take place., , Ravengard nods and unsheaths his sword into the looping idle sword held pointed down, hands close to chest. At the end of the line Gortash kneels down. looking at Ravenguard (Looping kneeling idle)"
												}
											},
