													"type": 23,
													"value": "[GERRY] Gortash strides towards the player from idle position left foot forward (down stairs) going from Stage 02 to Stage 03. Other Branch line to be delivered as he theatrically walks down the stairs - last line to be delivered in front of the player.. (GortashStridesDownstairsVersion03)"
